  "method": [
    "Sauté onion, shallot and bacon in butter for 5 minutes or until bacon is browned. Add wine and simmer uncovered,",
    "until wine evaporates.",
    "In a medium bowl, whisk eggs, cheese, pepper and parsley.",
    "Cook pasta as per the directions on the package; drain. Place pasta in a heated serving bowl and toss with egg",
    "mixture. Pour on bacon mix and toss.",
    "Serve while hot."
  ],
